    <title>Calculate 1932 voting breakdown</title>
    <statement>
      <p>Set up a formula for determining the number of respondents to the 1936 poll who said they voted in 1932 for either the Republican, Democratic, or Socialist or Other candidate. What proportion of these voted for the Republican candidate?</p>
